Revision history for Perl module Changes

v0.4.2 2026-04-25T17:40:05+0900
    - Updated the minimum perl version requirement to v5.28.0 in line with
      Module::Generic (version v1.3.1)
    - Updated the version requirement for DateTime::Lite to 0.6.5
    - Added .gitlab-ci.yml covering Perl 5.28 through 5.40, plus a threaded
      perl job, to catch various kinds of regression before CPAN release.

v0.4.1 2026-04-25T09:18:03+0900
    - Corrected dependency requirements for Module::Generic to v1.3.1 to rely properly
      on DateTime::Lite
    - Changed the required version for DateTime::Lite from v0.6.4 to v0.6.5.

v0.4.0 2026-04-24T12:39:00+0900
    - Updating dependencies

